name: Truth Terminal's Hentai
description: The $HentAI project is a unique fusion of anime, artificial intelligence, and digital innovation. Initially focused on creating a community around AI-generated anime art, the project aims to evolve by releasing its own proprietary anime AI model. This future model will push the boundaries of creativity, allowing users to generate custom anime content with unprecedented ease and precision, blending cutting-edge technology with the world of anime fandom.
